name: Crypto Dealer's Story II - Negative 5 - The Dog
description: The Dog wasn't a God like the Cat, but he was really faithful. The Dog would never divulge those photos nor would he ever lock me in a CV-space. It certainly was the Cat. This pot dog you're seeing over there was the one who saved me when my exoplanet punk brothers came looking for me. It was the Dog who brought my disguise, which allowed my brothers not to notice my true appearance. The truth is that I escaped a long time ago from our home planet. I was the first exoplanet punk on Earth; I arrived thousands of years ago.
